{"tid":700394,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現做人自私真係好開心","createTime":"2018-06-13T10:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T02:09:19.000Z","uid":58333,"like":104,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a30d11cbd40cd86517bff3bd3da6af583685e5","tid":700394,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"以前份人唔自私 好多時都會擺其他人係前面先<br />\n但慢慢發現不論係另一半 定係只係朋友<br />\n其實有人都係會唔珍惜<br />\n又無禮貌 愈幫得多就愈當我係工人咁<br />\n諗返起果陣真係傷心到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以就同自己講 自己以後唔可以再咁好<br />\n自己既好留俾屋企人已經夠<br />\n<br />\n一開始內心會有啲過意唔去<br />\n會成日有「其實我係咪應該幫佢？」「其實我咁係咪好衰？」等等既念頭<br />\n<br />\n但慢慢慣咗就唔會有野 發現個人舒服咗 爽咗好多 因為所有野都只係為自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦唔使再因為其他人唔珍惜/反轉豬肚就係屎 而唔開心<br />\n<br />\n而家自私慣咗 返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4128c3bc5d9ba91b887369d3580c543560db9340","tid":700394,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"慢慢改變自己"},{"pid":"a9630f8b90e622af0261d86e37ac2d3da34a47cf","tid":700394,"uid":158472,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"自己嘅好留俾屋企人已經足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84545fdbc61604aa6737bf07ac7c77e3f6c43a75","tid":700394,"uid":105507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"懂得先愛自己 先會有人對返自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85ebcad6c0d86ac6b3bf003db0d788d8f641c17","tid":700394,"uid":30708,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:18:24.000Z","msg":"對自己好就夠啦<br />\n你好撚叻咩"},{"pid":"c6c6c0ba3909ee3785e2219c1e0de268ffbd405d","tid":700394,"uid":58333,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"84545fdbc61604aa6737bf07ac7c77e3f6c43a75","tid":700394,"uid":105507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"re